          "target": "代码行开头的行号。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Show hidden characters such as tabs and line breaks.",
          "target": "显示隐藏字符，如制表符和换行符。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Converts URLs and emails in code to clickable links. Parses Markdown links in comments.",
          "target": "将代码中的 URL 和电子邮件转换为可点击链接。解析注释中的 Markdown 链接。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Makes tokens link to <a href=\"https://webplatform.github.io/docs/\">WebPlatform.org documentation</a>. The links open in a new tab.",
          "target": "使标记链接到 <a href=\\\"https://webplatform.github.io/docs/\\\">WebPlatform.org 文档</a>。链接将在新标签页中打开。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "This plugin allows you to prefix Prism's default classes (<code>.comment</code> can become <code>.namespace--comment</code>) or replace them with your defined ones (like <code>.editor__comment</code>). You can even add new classes.",
          "target": "此插件允许您为 Prism 的默认类添加前缀（例如 <code>.comment</code> 可以变为 <code>.namespace--comment</code>）或用您定义的类替换它们（如 <code>.editor__comment</code>）。您甚至可以添加新类。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Fetch external files and highlight them with Prism. Used on the Prism website itself.",
          "target": "获取外部文件并使用 Prism 进行高亮显示。在 Prism 网站本身上使用。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Display the highlighted language in code blocks (inline code does not show the label).",
          "target": "在代码块中显示高亮显示的语言（内联代码不显示标签）。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Fetch content with JSONP and highlight some interesting content (e.g. GitHub/Gists or Bitbucket API).",
          "target": "使用 JSONP 获取内容并高亮显示一些有趣的内容（例如 GitHub/Gists 或 Bitbucket API）。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Adds special CSS classes for each keyword matched in the code. For example, the keyword <code>if</code> will have the class <code>keyword-if</code> as well. You can have fine grained control over the appearance of each keyword by providing your own CSS rules.",
          "target": "为代码中匹配的每个关键字添加特殊的 CSS 类。例如，关键字 <code>if</code> 将同时具有类 <code>keyword-if</code>。您可以通过提供自己的 CSS 规则来精细控制每个关键字的外观。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Removes the initial line feed in code blocks.",
          "target": "删除代码块中的初始换行符。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Adds a small inline preview for colors in style sheets.",
          "target": "在样式表中为颜色添加小型内联预览。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Previewers for angles, colors, gradients, easing and time.",
          "target": "角度、颜色、渐变、缓动和时间的预览器。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Automatically loads the needed languages to highlight the code blocks.",
          "target": "自动加载所需的语言以高亮显示代码块。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Prevents custom markup from being dropped out during highlighting.",
          "target": "防止自定义标记在高亮显示过程中被丢弃。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Display a command line with a prompt and, optionally, the output/response from the commands.",
          "target": "显示带有提示符的命令行，并可选地显示命令的输出/响应。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Write markup without having to escape anything.",
          "target": "无需转义任何内容即可编写标记。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Supports multiple operations to normalize whitespace in code blocks.",
          "target": "支持多种操作来规范化代码块中的空白。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Highlights data-URI contents.",
          "target": "高亮显示 data-URI 内容。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Attach a toolbar for plugins to easily register buttons on the top of a code block.",
          "target": "附加一个工具栏，方便插件在代码块顶部注册按钮。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Add a button that copies the code block to the clipboard when clicked.",
          "target": "添加一个按钮，点击时将代码块复制到剪贴板。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "A button in the toolbar of a code block adding a convenient way to download a code file.",
          "target": "代码块工具栏中的一个按钮，提供便捷的代码文件下载方式。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Highlights matching braces.",
          "target": "高亮显示匹配的括号。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Highlights the code inside diff blocks.",
          "target": "高亮显示差异块内的代码。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Filters the elements the <code>highlightAll</code> and <code>highlightAllUnder</code> methods actually highlight.",
          "target": "筛选 <code>highlightAll</code> 和 <code>highlightAllUnder</code> 方法实际高亮显示的元素。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "A language with special styles to highlight file system tree structures.",
          "target": "一种具有特殊样式以高亮显示文件系统树状结构的语言。"
